OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry night
OL,6,Fwith clear spells, and overnight
OL,7,Ftemperatures a little fresher than of
OL,8,Flate especially in rural spots. One or
OL,9,Ftwo mist or fog patches developing in
OL,10,Fprone areas. Wind easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FDry with hazy sunshine and
OL,13,Fwarm or very warm for many again on
OL,14,FSaturday. However, cloud thickening
OL,15,Fduring the evening, with some
OL,16,Foutbreaks of occasionally heavy rain
OL,17,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
