OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FTurning
OL,6,Fmore unsettled and cooler into the
OL,7,Fstart of next week. Temperatures
OL,8,Fnearer normal for the time of year.
OL,9,FBecoming breezy with outbreaks of
OL,10,Foccasionally heavy rain or showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
